Package: sitemapr
Type: Package
Title: Parse and Validate XML Sitemaps
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Bart", "Turczynski", , "bartek@turczynski.pl", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8788-7980"))
Description: A deterministic toolkit for reading and validating XML, text, and
    index sitemaps against the Sitemap Protocol 0.9 and related W3C and RFC
    standards. It parses sitemap sources into tidy tibbles, expands sitemap
    indexes, and reports schema and protocol findings with stable, reproducible
    output.
